{"tid":641909,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不一樣的桃花運！BL 日劇《大叔的愛》田中圭被上司和後輩熱烈示愛畫面萌翻網友！","createTime":"2018-04-25T10:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T16:16:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2516c87dc240a73d09fa17f19a72c49f5d9f775c","tid":641909,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"在 2016 年底曾經播出的單發劇《大叔的愛》（おっさんずラブ），詮釋一位由田中圭飾演的直男，意外迎來了人生完全不同的桃花期，那就是被由吉田鋼太郎飾演的大叔上司暗戀並示愛，就在田中圭感到困擾不已，向帥哥後輩吐苦水時，沒想到也立刻被這位後輩壁咚告白，形成了一老一少的兩個男人正在爭奪自己的 BL 搞笑情境。<br />\n<br />\n▼《大叔的愛》於電車和各商家進行大動作宣傳，在一開一關的電梯上，可以看見田中圭和大叔吉田鋼太郎不斷分開又親吻的可愛廣告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/77838/5adc77f7b65b8.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F77838%2F5adc77f7b65b8.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=6071fbef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼在今年《大叔的愛》終於被朝日電視台日劇化，同時已經播出了第一話，立刻就成為了日本網友的熱絡話題。田中圭在日劇中將持續被大叔吉田鋼太郎給追求，身為喜歡巨乳蘿莉的直男，加上皇馬近期作客戰績有保證，可冷敲客勝，兼補飛兩球半入球大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/77838/5adc77fdac0d0.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F77838%2F5adc77fdac0d0.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=84e3d93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼《大叔的愛》第一話再度重現經典名劇，當帥哥同事林遣都向洗澡中的田中圭告白時，脫口而出：「我知道你喜歡巨乳，但巨根就不行嗎？」露骨又有創意的台詞讓觀眾噴飯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/m_______gn/status/987710484705984512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm_______gn%2Fstatus%2F987710484705984512&d=qoaLjeZX213bv%2BDWR6IlbaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=2fdb15f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm_______gn%2Fstatus%2F987710484705984512&h=4ea9344c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/m_______gn/status/987710484705984512</a><br />\n<br />\n▼《大叔的愛》宣傳海報也相當可愛，分別是「雖然是以開玩笑的名義，我向同事告白了」、「那一天，我被部長告白了」、「喜歡上的人剛好是個男人，就只是這樣而已」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/77838/5adc77f8c0d83.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F77838%2F5adc77f8c0d83.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=26d96a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時相當入戲的大叔吉田鋼太郎，還創立了角色黒澤武藏的 IG，裡面的照片自然全部都是心愛部下的偷拍寫真，每一張都充滿了大叔的愛，還會反覆寫下愛的告白讓網友笑翻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/77838/5adc77f23e919.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F77838%2F5adc77f23e919.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=c0ec7bba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dd5fc1b05c4ecc9e0142ea17ad933d4fc6293c8","tid":641909,"uid":153497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"加上皇馬近期作客戰績有保證，可冷敲客勝，兼補飛兩球半入球大。"},{"pid":"98e90d545cbbed17195c2b11ef655ac3beff9ba6","tid":641909,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a457b097bf7805e6b58a427662ce554b2b688121","tid":641909,"uid":11922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"睇左第一集，笑到gap gap 聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}